    "body": "⬆️ I removed the `ruleContexts`-related features from the connector and only commented the tests so that we can reuse them when we're ready to reimplement these features (I didn't `skip` the tests because TypeScript was complaining about the now non-existant `trackedFilters` and `transformRuleContexts` options).",
